Sentencas: A new method of obtaining gastight ceramic based on CaZr0.95Sc0.05O3-delta is presented.
Titulo: Composite Electrodes for Proton Conducting Electrolyte of CaZr0.95Sc0.05O3-δ

Sentencas: The microstructure and electric properties of the obtained samples, same as the behavior of composite electrodes in contact with this electrolyte, are studied for application of the obtained results in the technology of formation of electrochemical devices.
Titulo: Composite Electrodes for Proton Conducting Electrolyte of CaZr0.95Sc0.05O3-δ

Sentencas: The design of bilayer electrodes is suggested, in which the materials tested as the functional layer were layered lanthanum nickelate La2NiO4 (+) (delta) and substituted lanthanum nickelate La1.7Ca(Sr,Ba)(0.3)NiO4 (+ delta) in combination with the electrolyte components of Ce0.8Sm0.2O2 (-) (delta) and BaCe0.89Gd0.1Cu0.01O3 (- delta).
Titulo: Composite Electrodes for Proton Conducting Electrolyte of CaZr0.95Sc0.05O3-δ

Sentencas: The collector layer used was lanthanum nickelate-ferrite LaNi0.6Fe0.4O3 (- delta) and manganite La0.6Sr0.4MnO3 (- delta) that are characterized by high electron conductivity, low layer resistance and are close by their values of coefficient of linear thermal expansion to the materials of functional layers.
Titulo: Composite Electrodes for Proton Conducting Electrolyte of CaZr0.95Sc0.05O3-δ

Sentencas: Electrochemical activity of the obtained electrodes are compared with the characteristics of composite electrodes based on lanthanum ferrite-cobaltite La0.6Sr0.4Fe0.8Co0.2O3 (- delta) and deficient lanthanum manganite La0.75Sr0.2MnO3 (- delta).
Titulo: Composite Electrodes for Proton Conducting Electrolyte of CaZr0.95Sc0.05O3-δ
